      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't even know why i'm still doing this. the last three years of my phd feel like a complete waste. another failed trial, another grant rejected... i feel like i'm just running on empty and there's no finish line. i'm just so tired of trying to exist in this constant state of failure.",
