      "content": "It is okay to feel like the struggle is too much to bear; sometimes the only way to find peace is to stop fighting the weight. If you are thinking about ending your life or hurting yourself, please reach out to a crisis line or a medical professional immediately, as these thoughts are a signal that you need urgent support, not that you are beyond help. Your life has value even when it feels broken right now, and there are people who can sit with you in the silence until the noise fades.",
